phrases.phrase: 자라 보고 놀란 가슴 솥뚜껑 보고 놀란다
meanings: Once startled by a softshell turtle, you will also be startled by a caldron lid
(작은) a shrivelled-up penis, an impotent penis, (팽대하는) a deceptively small penis
